*Vašu* kuću je napravio majstor. (Your house was built by a craftsman.)

Moje dete obožava *vašu* decu. (My child loves your children.)

*Vašu* pomoć smo zahvalni. (We are thankful for your help.)

Želim da učestvujete u *vašoj* radionici. (I want you to participate in your workshop.)

*Vašu* poruku smo primili. (We received your message.)

Zahvalili smo se *vašem* gostoprimstvu. (We thanked you for your hospitality.)